      <title>伦敦劳合社因巴尔的摩大桥倒塌造成数十亿美元的保险损失</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/lloyds-london-sees-multi-billion-dollar-insurance-loss-baltimore-bridge-collapse-2024-03-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦劳合社 (SOLYD.UL) 董事长周四表示，巴尔的摩弗朗西斯·斯科特大桥的倒塌可能会导致数十亿美元的保险损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/lloyds-london-sees-multi-billion-dollar-insurance-loss-baltimore-bridge-collapse-2024-03-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 08:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
